step.parse_yaml:
Extract guardian configuration:
- file_read_guards[].name → {guard_names}
- file_read_guards[].description → {guard_descriptions}
- file_read_guards[].enforced → {guard_enforced}
- file_read_guards[].patterns[] → {guard_patterns} (array of regex)
- file_read_guards[].action → {guard_action}
- file_read_guards[].message → {guard_message}

task.integration:
This task is invoked by:
- workflow.xml step 0.6 (before profile loading)
- All agent file read operations (dex-master.md, etc.)
- Any workflow step that reads files from myDex/projects/


  When reading file: {file_path}
  1. Call guardian-check.xml with file_path parameter
  2. Check return: {access_allowed}
  3. If false → STOP and show user {access_denied_reason}
  4. If true → Proceed with normal file read
